name: Tabby Toys Industries
overview:
Established in the year 1986, at Delhi (India), we “Tabby Toys Industries” are known as the Manufacturer, Exporter and Supplier of an exclusive range of Dolls, Pug Dogs, Camel Toys, Dalmatian Dogs, Teddy Bear and Giraffe. Our offered range includes Aina Doll, Candy Doll, Anjali Doll, Dolphin fish, Duck, Horse, Fish, Bulldog Sleeping, Bulldog Sitting, Dawer Dog Sitting, Crazy Dog, Dalmation Sleeping, Dalmation Sitting, etc.

Our Quality Assurance: We offer a high quality array of products that is manufactured using high grade raw material and advanced technology in our well-developed manufacturing unit. At our organization, the entire production process is strictly monitored by our skilled quality analysts who have in-depth knowledge in this domain.

Why Us ?: International quality standard range Well equipped manufacturing facility Expert team of engineers, industrial designers and other supporting staff Customized packaging Competitive prices

Client Satisfaction: Client satisfaction is the most essential aspect, which we keep in our priority list. Our offered products are precisely fabricated using high grade raw material and latest technology in compliance with clients’ satisfaction. We successfully meet the variegated demands of clients by offering them products in custom made as well as in standard designs.

Our Team: Our team of skilled professionals works hard round the clock in order to manufacture, export and supply the high quality range of products. These professionals work in close-coordination with clients to comprehend their exact requirements and provide them as per the same.
